text: __NOTOC__ Mackenzie River may refer to: == Australia == *Mackenzie River (Queensland), a tributary of the Fitzroy River in Queensland *Mackenzie River (Victoria), in western Victoria, Australia, also called the McKenzie River, a tributary of the Wimmera River == Canada == * Mackenzie River, the longest river in Canada * Mackenzie River (Nova Scotia) == New Zealand == *Mackenzie River (New Zealand) in the South Island of New Zealand == See also == * McKenzie River (disambiguation) * SS Mackenzie River (1908), steamship on the Mackenzie River system
